title: 'Visibility of hands is low'
body: Purchased from Fastrack directly ... not via Amazon.in.  A superbly functional watch. Really big blackish dial. Very comfortable strap material. Not possible you will not love it.  Be warned though. Never came across a watch like this where the visibility of hands is low despite their white color over a contrasting black background. Reason ... hands are too lightly white and do not provide adequate background contrast. Problem to see the time in the dark by people wearing spectacles. Dial glass juts out a bit too.  Otherwise, one of the 'best bang for the buck' in the Indian watch market today. Very high value for money.
